<body>

	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 23px; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: Ubuntu; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 300; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 23px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
	<img alt="出国留学都能学到什么？" src="includes/sub_content/img/6358609955699460207223150.jpg"></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<b class="htitle">
<span>
加拿大快速通道移民系统(Express Entry)具有两个特点：<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<o:p></o:p></p>
<h1>
<span class="htitle">简单的申请条件，快速的审理时间。</span></h1>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span>
<span class="16">
加拿大快速通道移民</span></span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">（Express
Entry），是联邦技术移民（FSW）、技工移民（FST）、加拿大经验移民（CEC）等的甄选系统。候选人须获雇主聘书才可能获邀申请移民，最快半年内即可取得永久居民身分。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　- 不是所有人都可以进入EE：Express Entry 系统下，符合技术类（FSW），技工类（FST），经验类（CEC）的申请人才能进入 EE。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　- EE 并不改变原签证类别申请条件，但不按原项目评分标准进行排序，而是按照 CRS 体系排序，按分数高低顺序等待邀请 Invitation to
Apply (ITA) ，相当于双重过滤。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 21.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
Comprehensive Ranking
System（CRS）评价体系适合学历高，年龄轻，英语好的申请人，2015年后加拿大技术移民暂时取消了职业限制，只要英语好那么无论什么职业都可以申请，对年龄不占优势的申请人，雅思好同样很有机会。对于EE里评分不高的申请人如果职业好也有希望通过省提名移民。<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 21.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　提交加拿大EE是免费的，一个合格的EE在系统内会保留1年，过期只能重新提交。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　</span><b><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: bold; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">申请Express
Entry 的具体流程和周期是怎么样？</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<b>
<span class="htitle" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: bold; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　</span><span class="htitle">Express
Entry第一步：进入EE申请池</span></b><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　加拿大技术移民EE项目包括联邦独立技术移民、联邦经验类移民和联邦技工类移民，其中后两种移民类型不需要通过自我预评估表打分，可以直接提交EE，等待联邦移民局的邀请。任何人希望通过快速通道移民，必须先满足下面三个项目之一：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　- 技术类（FSW）：雅思4个6，够67分，最少一年0，A，B类职业工作经验；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　- 技工类（FST）：听说5，读3.5，写4,1年雇主offer或持有加拿大省政府的职业技工证书，近5年内有2年FST技工经验；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　- 经验类（CEC）：近3年内有1年加拿大0，A，B职业工作经验，B类职业雅思读4其他5，0，A类职业4个6（CLB7）。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　申请人满足这三个项目之一后，可以将自己的信息录入MyCIC账户（备注1），在线提交EE，注册Job Bank（备注2），等待移民局的邀请。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　备注1：建立EE账户需要的信息：1- 身份信息 2- 联系方式 3- 教育信息 4- 工作经验 5- 语言 6- 家人信息</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　备注2：Job Bank 是一个在线找工作的工具，根据申请人填写的个人信息，系统会自动为您提供合适的雇主和工作。申请人必须注册Job Bank,
除非已经获得Job Offer或者省提名了。如果申请人在递交EE之后的30天之内没有注册Job Bank, 申请人的EE将会过期。注册Job Bank
网址链接。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　</span>　<span class="htitle">Express
Entry第二步：申请雇主offer或省提名（不必须）</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(0,0,255);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　如果分数较低可以考虑通过加拿大雇主offer或EE下的省提名加600分，一旦申请人获得此项加分，基本上都会在在一个月左右收到联邦移民局的EE邀请，目前推荐海外申请人走的省提名EE项目有：</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　新斯科舍省提名Express Entry项目（2016年1月开放）</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　萨省提名Express Entry项目（2016年1月4日第一次发放500个配额）</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　安大略省提名Express Entry项目（EE-CRS评分400分以上可获得邀请）</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　</span>Express
Entry第三步：移民局邀请移民<span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(0,0,255);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　当移民局邀请的分数范围涵盖申请人的分数时，申请人可以获得移民局的移民邀请（ITA）。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　</span>　<span class="htitle">Express
Entry第四步：申请人递交正式的移民申请</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(0,0,255);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　申请人获得移民邀请ITA后，才可以递交正式的移民申请，此时</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　- 如果申请人在加拿大境内持有工签，可以申请桥梁工签（获得邀请之前不具备这样的条件）；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　- 若拒签，可以上诉（获得邀请之前没有递交移民申请，不能上诉）；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　- 移民局承诺6个月以内审理完毕（从递交之日算起）。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　</span><b><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: bold; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">EE周期：</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　邀请周期是根据申请人递交EE的时间，和得分高低决定的。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　EE新政后申请人获得邀请后会快速处理，大概半年内结案，这就是 Express Entry 的含义。但何时被邀请其实是决定整体周期的核心因素，也是不确定因素。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　-
如果EE申请人有雇主或省提名的600分加分基本可以在提交申请后一个月内获得邀请，这类申请人大概平均周期6个月，也就是很快（这里面没有考虑找雇主等待雇主审批及申请省提名的时间，加上这些时间大概平均周期在1年左右吧）。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　-
对EE下没有雇主或省提名的申请人，他们没有上面申请雇主或省提名的时间，有雅思和ECA(平均申请周期需要1-2个月)后可以直接提交EE等邀请，他们何时获得邀请关键要看他们自身分数在
Express Entry
系统内的排名及每次邀请的case数。对条件好的可能1-2个月就获得邀请，对条件一般的可能6个月8个月甚至10个月，对条件更差的可能1年EE过期后还无法获得邀请只能再次提交EE再次等待邀请。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　</span><b><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: bold; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">如何提高EE成功率</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　- 早提交，同样分数谁的早邀请谁（同样分数的人还是很多的）；</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　- 不断提高雅思，在ITA前可以不断更新EE系统，EE下雅思是单项加分的，单项提高0.5都可以提升竞争力。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　</span><b><span class="15" style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: bold; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">2016年加拿大技术移民
Express Entry 配额大幅减少</span></b><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　2016年加拿大计划接收30万新移民，比历年都多，其中难民和夫妻团聚移民配额增加较多，技术移民配额大幅减少；2016 年加拿大预计修改 EE
评分体系，有利于公民和永久居民的兄弟姐妹申请</span><span class="newStylep">加拿大移民</span><span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">。技术移民申请人需要早做打算。</span><span><o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class="p" style="margin-top: 0.0000pt; margin-right: 0.0000pt; margin-bottom: 11.2500pt; margin-left: 0.0000pt; text-indent: 0.0000pt; padding: 0pt 0pt 0pt 0pt; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; background: rgb(255,255,255);">
<span style="mso-spacerun: 'yes'; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(51,51,51); letter-spacing: 0.0000pt; font-weight: normal; text-transform: none; font-style: normal; font-size: 10.5000pt; mso-font-kerning: 0.0000pt; background: rgb(255,255,255); mso-shading: rgb(255,255,255);">
　　2016
年加拿大最新移民新政推翻了上任移民部长的多项移民政策，包括随行子女年龄的限制，入籍要求的限制，夫妻团聚移民等待期限的限制等；2016年加拿大将加速团聚移民审理速度。</span><span style="mso-spacerun:'yes';font-family:微软雅黑;color:rgb(51,51,51);letter-spacing:0.0000pt;font-weight:normal;text-transform:none;font-style:normal;font-size:10.5000pt;mso-font-kerning:0.0000pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p>

